            </ul>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong
              >{
                locale === "ko"
                  ? "연중 무휴, 언제, 어느 곳에서나 접속하여 은행업무 처리 가능"
                  : "Available 24/7, 365 days a year - access and conduct banking services anytime, anywhere"
              }</strong
