                  {
                    locale === "ko"
                      ? "암호화폐 실시간 현금화, 단일 수수료"
                      : "Real-time cryptocurrency conversion, single fee"
                  }
                </p>
                <p class="border-b border-white">
                  Single Account, single KYC, single regulatory authority
                </p>
                <p class="border-b border-white">
