                    locale === "ko"
                      ? "Fin-tech 및 Operation Company 설립, 스테이블코인생태계 선도백화점 상품권 RWA확보"
                      : "Leading stablecoin ecosystem with FinTech and RWAs"
                  }
                </p>
                <p class="border-b border-white">
                  {
                    locale === "ko"
                      ? "고객 신뢰 확보 & 금융 서비스 매출 증가"
                      : "Customer trust building & increased financial services revenue"
                  }
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>
              {
                locale === "ko"
                  ? "은행업무를 쉽게 처리할 수 있는 UI/UX 사용"
                  : "User-friendly UI/UX to perform banking operations"
              }
